      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Esportazione [adc]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-adc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "azi "               to   f-xxx-are              .
           move      "adc "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
           move      "std_azi_adc"        to   f-xxx-npe              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
