      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-adc-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sel su [adc]                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-adc-tip-con       =    "SEP"
                     go to exe-exp-adc-200.
       exe-exp-adc-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
