      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-adc-tip-arc       to   w-exe-con-arc          .
           move      rf-adc-cod-arc       to   w-exe-con-cod          .
           move      rf-adc-num-prg       to   w-exe-con-prg          .
           move      rf-adc-dpz-arc       to   w-exe-con-dpz          .
           move      rf-adc-ide-dat       to   w-exe-con-idd          .
           move      rf-adc-ide-ute       to   w-exe-con-idu          .
           move      rf-adc-ide-fas       to   w-exe-con-idf          .
           move      rf-adc-tip-con       to   w-exe-con-tip          .
           move      rf-adc-des-key       to   w-exe-con-dsk          .
           move      80                   to   w-exe-con-lun          .
           move      rf-adc-num-con       to   w-exe-con-num          .
           move      rf-adc-int-con       to   w-exe-con-int          .
           move      rf-adc-dat-agg       to   w-exe-con-agg          .
           perform   exe-exp-con-000      thru exe-exp-con-999        .
       exe-exp-adc-750.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a Next su [adc]                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
